OL,3,CGeopolitics and sport collide as Iran
OL,4,Cprepare to play in Los Angeles
OL,6,FFrom the White House last night,
OL,7,FDonald Trump announced a deal with
OL,8,FIran that will be signed on Friday in
OL,9,FGeneva.
OL,11,FBut here in Los Angeles, it is a
OL,12,Fdifferent story. Tonight on the pitch,
OL,13,FIran's national team plays its opening
OL,14,FWorld Cup group match against New
OL,15,FZealand amid controversy and protests.
OL,17,FIran's players have already arrived
OL,18,Fhere ahead of the game. It's a moment
OL,19,Fof real tension.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
