OL,3,CGeopolitics and sport collide as Iran
OL,4,Cprepare to play in Los Angeles
OL,6,FIran claims that the US government has
OL,7,Fbroken the spirit of the competition.
OL,9,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FEarlier this month, Iran moved its
OL,15,Ftraining base to northern Mexico to
OL,16,Fminimise time in the US.
OL,18,FSeveral of the Iranian support team
OL,19,Fhave been denied visas. And the
OL,20,Fplayers fear a hostile reception when
OL,21,Fthe national anthem is played.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
