OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781592466
OL,3,CGeopolitics and sport collide as Iran
OL,4,Cprepare to play in Los Angeles
OL,6,FThey have every reason to believe they
OL,7,Fare playing in the lion's den. That's
OL,8,Fbecause Los Angeles has the largest
OL,9,Fcommunity of Iranians outside of Iran
OL,10,Fitself.
OL,12,FMany were forced to flee after the
OL,13,F1979 Islamic revolution and are
OL,14,Fimplacably opposed to the regime.
OL,16,FThe city has even been nicknamed
OL,17,F"Tehran-geles" for its huge number of
OL,18,Fdiaspora Iranians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
