OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781592466
OL,3,CGeopolitics and sport collide as Iran
OL,4,Cprepare to play in Los Angeles
OL,6,FWe have spoken to Iranian-Americans
OL,7,Fhere who will be cheering not for Iran
OL,8,Fbut for New Zealand. They believe
OL,9,FIran's team is a propaganda machine
OL,10,Ffor the regime and in no way
OL,11,Frepresents the nation.
OL,13,FThousands of protesters will be
OL,14,Fgathering outside the stadium. They
OL,15,Fwill be flying the Lion and Sun flag,
OL,16,Fwhich is a symbol of pre-
OL,17,Frevolutionary, monarchist Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
