OL,3,CGeopolitics and sport collide as Iran
OL,4,Cprepare to play in Los Angeles
OL,6,FFifa, under rules that insist that no
OL,7,Fpolitical symbols are allowed, has
OL,8,Fsaid that these historic Iranian flags
OL,9,Fcannot be waved in the stadium.
OL,11,FThere is a further twist. If the
OL,12,FUnited States and Iran both come out
OL,13,Fof their groups in second place, they
OL,14,Fwill meet each other in the round of
OL,15,F32.
OL,17,FThat match would be a geopolitically
OL,18,Ffraught sporting contest for the ages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
